‹A celebration of life Dr Richard Edward Motie
13th March 1971 - 28th September 2013
A true gentleman with a big heart and warm personality.
it broke our hearts when you died but you did not depart alone.
A part of us went with you, wherever you may roam.
Till memories fade and life departs, you live forever in our hearts.
I will miss you each day until we meet again.
Goodbye my love, sweet dreams and love you to the moon and back. - HP
Dad - always and forever in my heart and with me. Love, your princess. - SM"–
